data.description: Welcome to the serene area of Silver Ridge Estates where the views will make you fall in love! A large Trex deck was added to truly enjoy the beauty. Plenty of space inside and out of this triple wide manufactured home on 5 acres. This home features three spacious bedrooms and two and half baths. The primary has a bonus office/library area attached in addition to a large bathroom. There is also an additional storage/bonus room off the kitchen that was used as a bedroom. There are two living areas, vaulted ceilings throughout, a walk-in pantry, and a large kitchen with a bar for entertaining.  This is a great place for your hobby farm the outside has animals, a barn with stalls, chicken coop, and a fire pit. This home has so much to offer. Sellers willing to acceptable all loan types, including assumable. Call to schedule your showing today!
